    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface UIUtils.CreateLabelCallback<LabelType>

    Interface to create label for the UIUtils.collectFields(Localizer, Class, Object, List, CreateLabelCallback, CreateFieldCallback) method call. Especially designed for using with the lambdas
